trans-unit.source: The SAF-T (Standard Audit File - Tax) is a standard file format for exporting various types of accounting transactional data using the XML format. This guide helps you set up SAF-T for the Norwegian version of Dynamics 365 Business Central. If you do not have a chart of accounts, this guide helps you to create it based on SAF-T standard chart of accounts. If you do not want to set this up right now, close this page.
